ReticlePC Open Source Software License

End User Rules:
1. You may not redistribute this software at a price.
2. You may redistribute the source or compiled versions, modified or not, but you must credit the origional distributor.
3. If you had to pay for the source, you may not redistribute the source. If you do it must be heavily modified.
4. If you redistribute this software, modified or not, you must keep this license on it unless allowed to do otherwise by the original distributor.

Distributor Rules:
1. You may not put a price on the compiled distribution of this software.
2. You may optionally charge money for the source code, although not advised.